subsection.def:
plant
                    (工業裝置) includes any plant, equipment, gear,
                machinery, apparatus, or appliance, or any part thereof;

paragraph.content:
is apprenticed to that contractor or to any other contractor engaged in
                    work at that site, under a contract of apprenticeship registered under the
                    Apprenticeship Ordinance (Cap. 47);

has completed an apprenticeship and possesses a certificate of completion
                    issued under the Apprenticeship Ordinance (Cap.
                    47);
